    "3f55f60c-2189-402d-a28a-fd053125c22a": {"id":"3f55f60c-2189-402d-a28a-fd053125c22a","project_id":24447,"key":83432262,"version":null,"meta":{},"children":[],"deleted_at":null,"created_at":"2023-11-28T18:33:18.334Z","updated_at":"2023-11-28T18:33:18.334Z","props":{"useBackgroundControls":true,"enableTextToSpeechBtn":true,"content":"\u003cp data-type=\"paragraph\"\u003eFriable asbestos breaks down easily. It can be crumbled by the pressure of your hands or when dry. This is the most dangerous type of asbestos because it releases tiny particles into the air when it breaks down which increases the risk. Examples of friable asbestos:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul class=\"chameleon-ul\" data-type=\"bulleted-list\"\u003e\u003cli class=\"chameleon-li\" data-type=\"list-item\"\u003ePipe insulation \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"chameleon-li\" data-type=\"list-item\"\u003eAsbestos rope\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"chameleon-li\" data-type=\"list-item\"\u003ePopcorn ceiling \u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-type=\"paragraph\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-type=\"paragraph\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-type=\"bold\"\u003eHRV never disturbs or works with friable asbestos\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},"type":"Text"}, 
